Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.23,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,MARRIAGETOXIN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.87,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PERTEMUAN HIMA KAMPING UNIVERSITAS SHINEI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.32,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PUTRA KEDUA: MITSUHIKO, PUTRI SULUNG: FUTAE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.69,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,MENDIANG PUTRA SULUNG: KAZUHITO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.25,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KARTU IDENTITAS MAHASISWA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.75,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,NAMA: OSHIMA DAIGO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.21,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PERTEMUAN HIMA KAMPING UNIVERSITAS SHINEI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.92,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,[RELAKSASI MAKSIMAL] ASMR PAMAN ALPS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.10,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,MARRIAGETOXIN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.06,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PENGGUNA SUARA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.71,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TIGA HARI LAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:02.39,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,ORIENTASI FAKULTAS EKONOMI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:41.99,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,ORIENTASI FAKULTAS EKONOMI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.03,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,SATU HARI LAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.94,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KEBAKARAN MISTERIUS TERUS BERLANJUT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:56.00,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TUAN CHLADNI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka yang terus mengasah\Nseni pembunuhan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}para "Pengguna".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah melalui garis keturunan\Nyang sangat panjang,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka mendapat teknik mematikan\Nyang disebut "Mutasi Keturunan".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kisah salah satu dari mereka,\NGero Hikaru sang Pengguna Racun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero Hikaru sang Pengguna Racun\Nuntuk mencari jodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf menunggu lama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lemon sour pesanannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero aman tidak, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ini pesta penyambutan maba\Nyang legendaris itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kusangka jadi lokasi\Nkerjaku kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak baru, ayo kumpul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merayakan penerimaan masuk universitas\Ndan pertemuan kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ayo bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu anak tahun pertama, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?\NAcara sambutannya asyik tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ashik...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ashik shekalih...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai nanti, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal senior sudah mengajakku ngobrol...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin memintamu mengawal\Nkeponakanku yang mulai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi mahasiswa musim semi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sebisa mungkin jangan\Nterlihat mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Ureshino Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahnya yang adalah kakakku,\Nsudah mendirikan perusahaan ini dari nol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi setahun lalu\Nmeninggal karena sakit keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meninggalkan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- wasiat agar putrinya, Shiori,\N- Yes, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- mewarisi perusahaan ini saat sudah dewasa.\N- Keep it going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, ada orang yang tidak suka\Ndengan keputusan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yaitu kakak perempuanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia merasa hak waris Balzak adalah miliknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tidak tahu cara apa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang akan dilakukan Futae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut rumor,\Ndia menyewa pengguna teknik aneh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang tidak bisa ditandingi\Norang terlatih pada umumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, terima kasih banyak sudah mau\Nmenerima permintaan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kartu identitas mahasiswamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai hari ini, kamu mahasiswa tahun ketiga\Nbernama Oshima Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku langsung ingin minta tolong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin coba datang ke pesta minum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa malah sengaja\Nmau ikut pesta minum?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa boleh buat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, selanjutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Da-Dari Fakultas Ekonomi tahun pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Ureshino Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat seperti ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- harus bahas topik apa?\N- Gim kesukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Fakta generasiku.\N- Gim kesukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Fakta generasiku.\N- Garis pantai Ria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Asal.\N- Kalimat lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kisah cinta, penurunan angka kelahiran.\N- Sinetron, Keshogunan Edo, hobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Angkat barbel dengan kemiringan,\N- Mekanika kuantum, festival kampus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- putus cinta, makanan yang dibenci.\N- Mekanika kuantum, festival kampus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sa-Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, silakan selanjutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero sanggup ikut pesta minum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah berulang kali minum\Nbersama Pengguna Serangga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bikin khawatir saja,\Naku ikut menyusup, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutunjukkan bahwa pengguna ulung\Njuga ahli memeriahkan pesta minum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oshima Daigo dari Fakultas Ekonomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuminum delapan gelas\Ndalam sekali tenggak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang bukan zamannya begituan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertunjukan utamanya baru dari sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa sebaiknya panggil ambulans?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti dapat tepuk tangan meriah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini polimer superabsorben!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bahaya untuk tubuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah jadi bencana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang belum perkenalan tinggal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu dipanggil, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Naruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, bisa beri tahu nama lengkap\Natau dari fakultas mana—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang jauh lebih penting dari itu adalah\Nbisa bertemu kalian di momen ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku super berterima kasih pada takdir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan dia itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari tadi cuma meditasi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Super terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak jelas banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa diulang dua kali?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dialah sosok yang ditakdirkan untukku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naruko, sebelahmu masih kosong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau diterima dengan baik\Nkayak begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang gara-gara muka, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesta minum ternyata serumit itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Upah per jamnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ureshino, kamu ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, ma-maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero, jangan malah bikin dia nangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balas dendam kegagalanmu tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum bilang apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah tidak usah terlalu\Nmemaksakan diri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau mengatasi kelemahan berkomunikasi\Nkarena akan mewarisi perusahaan orang tua,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu jadi memaksakan diri\Nikut pesta minum, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}He-Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku sangat senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah memikirkan perasaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada hubungannya dengan perusahaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bisa berbaur dengan teman-teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di saat-saat terakhirnya Ayah bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cobalah minum alkohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi setelah umurmu 20 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shiori, kamu itu anak yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kamu terlalu sungkan pada orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kalau pikiran rumit\Nyang berputar-putar di kepalamu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan lebih menarik kalau diluapkan semuanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kamu bisa bergembira\Nbersama orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah harapan Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aya—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat merasa waktunya tepat,\Nkepalaku malah dibanjiri kata-kata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ureshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kalau yang penting\Nharus coba melangkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau semua orang juga akan menerimaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski di kepala tahu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah terpikir apa aslinya mereka\Nmerasa muak, marah, atau sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya aku tetap tidak bisa\Nbicara banyak dengan Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa sempat tanya kenapa\Ndiriku yang seperti ini jadi pewaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya, aku ingin melatih diriku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar rasa takut bisa kuempaskan\Ndengan tertawa lepas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyawamu itu diincar, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku tidak akan melarang\Nkalau ada tempat yang ingin kamu datangi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tugasku adalah melindungimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Madam, aku ingin melapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengawalnya super hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu natural,\Nseolah tiada celah sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Super lupa buat isi daya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bercanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah satu bulan tapi belum ada kemajuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pikir sudah kubayar berapa dirimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Posisi top perusahaan alat pesta\Ndengan kapitalisasi pasar 1,5 triliun yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mana bisa dipegang anak gadis seperti dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan akan kamu habisi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum waktunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apanya yang belum waktunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah satu bulan lebih—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengawal bernama Oshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kuat dia bukan siapa-siapa, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengguna sepertimu pasti bisa\Nmembunuhnya dalam sekejap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Madam, akan super kutepati janjinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, buat dia melepas sendiri\Nhak warisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika itu tidak memungkinkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paling parahnya, kamu bunuh saja dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero, ini cuma pura-pura jadi mahasiswa,\Nbukannya tidak perlu serius mendengarkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya buatku,\Njadinya terasa asyik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa lalumu tragis dan menyedihkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besok...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang kamu yang di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri contoh produk\Nyang jadi titik balik industrinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Campur Aduk Melimpah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Produk langka yang hanya diproduksi\N100 buah untuk perayaan 30 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kamu paham juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembuka pasar Campur Aduk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembali ke dasar produk Campur Aduk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain, Campur Aduk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melimpah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada mahasiswa dengan\Nsemangat sebesar dirimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa tenang kuserahkan ke generasi selan—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku tidak pernah menjauh dari target,\Ndia mau pakai cara paksa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang mencurigakan di dalam kelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari luar, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sudah selalu kupastikan\Ntidak ada orang di jangkauan tembak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serangan serentak dengan area luas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi, area ini punya ventilasi yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti bukan serangan gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu artinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Langsung bisa bergerak setelah\Nmenyuntikkan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:15:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengirim gelombang suara dari jarak jauh\Nuntuk menggetarkan orang dan ruangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memulihkan keseimbangan\Nyang terganggu secara super instan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Normalnya itu tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang bisa melakukan sesuatu seluas\Ndan serumit itu dengan presisi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang bisa meracik ramuan seperti itu\Nsecara instan adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pengguna Suara!\N- Pengguna Racun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kulaporkan ke klien.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditutupi sebagai kecelakaan\Nuntuk meredam keributan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aturan keras seorang asasin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ureshino, ini serius ingin membunuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gero, berarti harus absen dari kamp besok?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tergantung keputusan klien.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja boleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah lama menantikan kamp itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sahabat semasa kuliah adalah permata\Nyang tidak ada duanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buatlah yang banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asal diserahkan ke mereka berdua,\Nkamu tidak usah khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudah, Paman, aku berangkat dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuat kalian menunggu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bawaanmu sebesar itu,\Nmemang apa isinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, ada payung lipat terus, rahasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdiam diri di dalam rumah pun\Nbelum pasti aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, solusinya harus\Nberhadapan dengan musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini beda dari kasus Himekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang tahu kapan\NPengguna Suara akan menyerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mau dia selesaikan saat kamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, ini apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janji yang super penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naruko panutan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau berjanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, janji sama aku juga, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ah, curang!\N- Super penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria yang bisa masak itu\Ntiga kali lipat lebih populer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut penelusuran pribadi Kinosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutunjukkan teknik memasak kelas satu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, apa ada... yang mau yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang... mau yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yakisoba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Kinosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak perlu mengkhawatirkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ureshino sendiri yang bilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya mau diatasi\Ndengan kemampuannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bagaimana caranya berbaur dengan semuanya?\N- Yakisoba, saus, mi, tepung terigu, jahe merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubis, air, sumpit sekali pakai, pohon betula.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapioka, hukum aset pribadi, trik sulap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak bisa mengajak ngobrol...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakai cara yang lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa gadis sihir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada rahasia atau trik tersembunyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang akan kumulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pampuru, pimpuru, pamupop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pimpuru, pampuru, pamupop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Wah!\N- Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, akan kukeluarkan porsi jumbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pimpuru, pampuru, pamupop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yakin tidak apa-apa, tuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ureshino, trik sulapmu hebat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu produk perusahaan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru pertama kali kutunjukkan\Nke depan semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah gagal di akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pandai bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, teringat pertunjukan Gero\Ndi pesta minum tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi kepikiran ide ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cie, cie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bantu apa-apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lo? Kenapa, nih?\N- Tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, kalian tahu tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kisah Kutukan Tuan Chladni.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat ini awalnya desa terbengkalai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya sebelum perang,\Nselalu ada persembahan untuk dewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa tahun sekali saat panen buruk,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan memilih anak\Nyang usianya paling kecil di desa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, anak itu akan dikurung di kuil itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah perang,\Ntradisi itu memang ditinggalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kerap terjadi bencana seperti
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tanah longsor dan kebakaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jumlah penduduk di masa jayanya\Nyang hampir mendekati 1000 jiwa,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekarang lenyap tak bersisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, hingga saat ini Tuan Chladni\Nmasih menunggu persembahannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adalah kamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu bohong, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oshima, justru culun kalau\Nbereaksi dingin begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Ureshino.\NItu semua benar adanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bikin suasananya mungkin sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ayo segera dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uji nyali yang sudah kalian tunggu-tunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Eh?\N- Sumpah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malas, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, ada yang lihat Naruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pengin berpasangan sama dia\Nbuat keliling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melodi hutan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah super siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ureshino Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita mulai sesi luar biasa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari jeritanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Super mustahil untuk lari.\N- Apa yang, wah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai jatuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kondisiku super sempurna.\N- Kesempatan begini harus dimanfaatkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Harus super dinikmati.\N- Polimer superabsorben!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, Tuan Chladni.
